<%= render "navbar" %>
<section class="proje">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="header text-center"><span>Watch List</span></h1>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">
        <div class="proje-info">
          <p class="text p-skills"> Ruby | Ruby on Rails | Html | Css | JavaScript | Cloudinary | Heroku | PostgreSQL </p>
          <p class="text">Watch list is basic MVC models web application that allows users create their own watchlist.</p>
          <div class="project-btn">
            <%= link_to "See Project", 'https://watchlist-b567.herokuapp.com//', target: 'blank', class: 'btn' %>
            <%= link_to "See Code", 'https://github.com/Sevil-h/rails-watch-list', target: 'blank', class: 'btn' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-carousel">
          <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="3"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="4"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="5"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="6"></li>
              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="7"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/index.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Watch list connect the movie lovers who wants to create own watch list and can see the their watch list.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/index1.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>It has been used Css animation to change the image on home page that looks like a gif.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/addanewlist.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Movie lovers can create own Movie List to the website along with a photo which is uploaded to Cloudinary. </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/mylist.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Movie lovers can see their movie list can click thought to see movies related to the list.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/movies.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('addamoviebtn.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('addamovie.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Movie lovers can add movie their movie list. And this movies has been stored PostSQL via scrapping APIs. </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/bookmark.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/info2.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Movie lovers can see the rating, poster and overview about the movies that used APIs stored the information.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="<%= image_path('watchlist/info.png') %>" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
<%= render "footer" %>
